---
title: Honey Sriracha Chicken Thigh with Stir-Fried Veggies
description: Tender chicken thighs get a sweet-heat spin with a honey-sriracha glaze! Ginger, garlic and crispy shallots bring big savoury flavours to fluffy jasmine rice.
